 * Returns an object you can spread into the request `config`.
 *
 * Budgets (Gemini 2.5 Pro/Flash):
 *   off    → thinkingBudget: 0  (disables thinking)
 *   low    → 1024
 *   medium → 8192
 *   high   → 24576 (Flash hard cap; Pro accepts up to 32768)
